%%{init: {'theme': 'default'}}%%
flowchart TD
    A([Normal Operation]) --> B{Failure Trigger}
    B -->|Timeout|      C[Retry with back-off]
    B -->|Error rate|   D[Circuit Breaker Opens]
    B -->|Queue full|   E[Backpressure / Shedding]

    C --> F{Retry success?}
    F -->|Yes| G([Recovered])
    F -->|No|  H[Dead-Letter Queue]

    D --> I[Fallback Response]
    E --> J[429 / Drop Request]

    style A fill:#9f9,stroke:#333
    style G fill:#9f9,stroke:#333
    style H fill:#f99,stroke:#333
    style J fill:#f99,stroke:#333
